            "value": "%3Cp%3EWhat%20a%20stewardship%20we%20have!%20Paul%20said%20that%20he%20was%20Christ's%20servant%2C%20entrusted%20with%20the%20secret%20things%20of%20God.%20Similarly%2C%20Ezra%20and%20his%20men%20were%20told%20to%20deliver%20unto%20the%20God%20of%20Jerusalem%20those%20things%20that%20were%20entrusted%20to%20them%20for%20worship%20in%20God's%20temple%20(Ezra%207%3A19).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJust%20as%20the%20precious%20gold%20and%20silver%20articles%20of%20the%20temple%20were%20entrusted%20to%20Ezra%2C%20so%20we%20have%20been%20entrusted%20with%20the%20deep%20secrets%20of%20the%20doctrines%20of%20God%3A%20justification%2C%20sanctification%2C%20and%20glorification.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%22Now%2C%20a%20person%20who%20is%20put%20in%20charge%20as%20a%20manager%20must%20be%20faithful%22%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E(1%20Corinthians%204%3A2)%2C%20and%20we%20are%20to%20treasure%20the%20truths%20we%20have%20been%20given%20by%20the%20Holy%20Spirit.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ENo%20careless%20hands%20touched%20the%20precious%20temple%20articles%2C%20but%20they%20were%20carefully%20preserved%20and%20protected%20until%20they%20reached%20Jerusalem.%20We%20must%20reverently%20carry%20the%20truths%20of%20the%20Christian%20faith%2C%20viewing%20them%20as%20more%20precious%20than%20gold%2C%20silver%2C%20or%20diamonds.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ELet%20us%20hold%20the%20gifts%2C%20doctrines%2C%20and%20ministries%20we%20have%20received%20with%20faithful%20hands%2C%20and%20one%20day%20we%20will%20deliver%20them%20safely%20to%20the%20New%20Jerusalem%20and%20present%20them%20to%20the%20One%20who%20entrusted%20us%20with%20them.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
